Package: docker-scraper
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Andrew Spence
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, docker.io | docker-ce
Description: Docker Event Scraper - Monitors container creation events
 This service monitors Docker container creation events and logs
 their metadata to JSON files for ingestion into Splunk or other
 log management systems.
